{"questionId":"11895","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>This question will diagonalize a matrix and apply this to the transformation of a curve.</p>\n<p>Let the matrix&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"M = \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {\\tfrac{5}{2}}&amp;{\\tfrac{1}{2}} \\\\   {\\tfrac{1}{2}}&amp;{\\tfrac{5}{2}}  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mi>M</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n                <mfrac>\n                  <mn>5</mn>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </mfrac>\n              </mstyle>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n                <mfrac>\n                  <mn>1</mn>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </mfrac>\n              </mstyle>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n                <mfrac>\n                  <mn>1</mn>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </mfrac>\n              </mstyle>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n                <mfrac>\n                  <mn>5</mn>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </mfrac>\n              </mstyle>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Let&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {\\tfrac{1}{{\\sqrt 2 }}}&amp;{\\tfrac{1}{{\\sqrt 2 }}}  \\end{array}} \\\\   {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {\\tfrac{{ - 1}}{{\\sqrt 2 }}}&amp;{\\tfrac{1}{{\\sqrt 2 }}}  \\end{array}}  \\end{array}} \\right) = {{\\mathbf{R}}^{ - 1}}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n                <mtr>\n                  <mtd>\n                    <mrow>\n                      <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n                        <mfrac>\n                          <mn>1</mn>\n                          <mrow>\n                            <msqrt>\n                              <mn>2</mn>\n                            </msqrt>\n                          </mrow>\n                        </mfrac>\n                      </mstyle>\n                    </mrow>\n                  </mtd>\n                  <mtd>\n                    <mrow>\n                      <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n                        <mfrac>\n                          <mn>1</mn>\n                          <mrow>\n                            <msqrt>\n                              <mn>2</mn>\n                            </msqrt>\n                          </mrow>\n                        </mfrac>\n                      </mstyle>\n                    </mrow>\n                  </mtd>\n                </mtr>\n              </mtable>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n                <mtr>\n                  <mtd>\n                    <mrow>\n                      <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n                        <mfrac>\n                          <mrow>\n                            <mo>−</mo>\n                            <mn>1</mn>\n                     